Centenarians and supercentenarians: a black swan. Emerging social, medical and 
surgical problems.

Vacante M(1), D'Agata V, Motta M, Malaguarnera G, Biondi A, Basile F, 
Malaguarnera M, Gagliano C, Drago F, Salamone S.

