The Black Swan Theory was described by Nassim Nicholas Taleb in his book "The 
Black Swan". This theory refers to "high-impact, hard-to-predict, and rare 
events beyond the realm of normal expectations". According to Taleb's criteria, 
a Black Swan Event is a surprise, it has a major impact and after the fact, the 
